    <chapter>    
        <title>Introduction</title>
        <para>JStock a free stock market software which supports multiple countries' stock market. The below are a list of JStock's highlighted features :</para>

        <para>
            <orderedlist>
                <listitem><para>Multiple countries' stock market. Currently, there are 12 countries supported. They are Denmark, France, Germany, Italy, India, Malaysia, Norway, Singapore, Spain, Sweden, United Kingdom and United State.</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Real-Time stock info. You will able to monitor all your favorite stocks movement, within single page.</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Stock indicator editor. You will able to compose your own indicator rule, with simple drag-n-drop graphical blocks. There are no programming required.</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Stock indicator scanner. You will able to perform real-time indicator scanning, to filter out thousands of stocks from the entire stock market. You may also receive email and system tray message alert whenever a stock is being found.</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Portfolio management. You will able to know your most up-to-date net worth, by recording down your buy and sell records.</para></listitem>
                <listitem><para>Market chit chat. You may chat with other JStock users on the hottest market news, in an easy and fun way.</para></listitem>
            </orderedlist>            
        </para>
    </chapter>

